m r newlin currently lead independent director for meritor and a member of the compensation and management development committee and the corporate governance and nominating committee has been elected to serve as nonexecutive chairman of the board newlin has been chairman and a director of newlin investment company llc since april  he retired as chairman of the board of kennametal inc in  prior to that newlin served as executive vice president and chief administrative officer of dicks sporting goods inc until his retirement in march  about meritormeritor inc is a leading global supplier of drivetrain mobility braking and aftermarket solutions for commercial vehicle and industrial markets with more than a year legacy of providing innovative products that offer superior performance efficiency and reliability the company serves commercial truck trailer offhighway defense specialty and aftermarket customers around the world meritor is based in troy mich united states and is made up of approximately  diverse employees who apply their knowledge and skills in manufacturing facilities engineering centers joint ventures distribution centers and global offices in  countries meritor common stock is traded on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol mtor for important information visit the companys website at wwwmeritorcom logo  httpphotosprnewswirecomprnhdelogo   to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesivorjikeevanstostepdownasexecutivechairmanofmeritorhtml source meritor inc related links httpwwwmeritorcom may    et preview meritor reports secondquarter fiscal year  results apr    et preview meritor hosts conference call and webcast to present fiscal year  secondquarter earnings results my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen also from this source jul    et meritor appoints cheri lantz vice president and chief strategy jul    et rev group inc and meritor® announce new standard supplier explore more news releases 